{"tid":209131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭錦滿否認盜竊9本圖書　案件下月中進行審前覆核","createTime":"2017-04-20T03:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T19:47:26.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d64df578e4c74e7d0f8b7380c8ca4012eb3ff93a","tid":209131,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"熱血公民鄭錦滿涉嫌於去年3月在九龍圖書館偷取9本圖書，被控盜竊罪，案件在九龍城裁判法院再次提堂，鄭錦滿不認罪。<br />\n<br />\n控方指，案中共有9名證人，1段被告在社交網站面書的75秒片段，以及圖書館閉路電視錄影的1小時35分鐘片段。<br />\n<br />\n由於鄭錦滿不認罪，法官安排在5月12日進行審前覆核，並准許以同樣條件承擔，但由於他早前另一宗案件藐視法庭罪成，被判入獄3個月，他最早5月30日出獄，需要繼續服刑。"},{"pid":"ab920c249c60a48748352ebc6fa21af24e31ec67","tid":209131,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:40:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政</span></span>"},{"pid":"c148151b9d5c04a02483a8f1bdae575d979958fd","tid":209131,"uid":90791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3aa37dcefbc8fb65daa9f5babb45597e5d33c41","tid":209131,"uid":84633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:44:43.000Z","msg":"竊書不能算偷&hellip;&hellip;竊書！&hellip;&hellip;讀書人的事，能算偷麼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9aeb4d76055a4303e52bac88ec2a81d4c031424","tid":209131,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T03:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2a27848aaffb0c4dc434006d64a4c1bf001a4b7","tid":209131,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislik